File Sharing application


Web Server (Google Drive )

user will upload the file to our server POST (http://localhost:8080/api/files/)
genrate a shareable link (GET http://localhost:8080/files/:uuid)
use the link to download the file (GET http://localhost:8080/files/download/:uuid)
email notification to downloadable  (POST http://localhost:8080/api/files/send)

multer :
1. creating a multer instance 
2. create a configuration object
3. attach the middleware to required API or Module or App

Where to Save the file ? (location)
file validations? (single / multiple)
